Package: pegasus.v2f
Title: R Client for PEGASUS V2F Gene Prioritization Databases
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sam", "Sheffield", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "ssheffi1@jhu.edu")
Description: Read-only R client for querying PEGASUS V2F gene prioritization
    databases. Connects to DuckDB or PostgreSQL databases built by the v2f
    Python CLI and returns data frames. Provides domain-first functions for
    searching genes, browsing evidence, and exploring GWAS loci.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
